OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,F'Emily' was initially offered an
OL,7,F"insulting" #30 refund from Travelodge
OL,8,Fin compensation, which they later
OL,9,Fadmitted was inappropriate, as Good
OL,10,FMorning Britain's Ashna Hurynag reports
OL,12,F"It's literally easier to get into a
OL,13,Fhotel room where someone is asleep and
OL,14,Fvulnerable, than it is to get into a
OL,15,Fnightclub."
OL,17,F'Emily' is speaking from experience.
OL,19,FShe was sexually assaulted by a man
OL,20,Fwho gained access to her hotel room
OL,21,Fwhilst she slept.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FWe have changed her name to protect
OL,7,Fher identity.
OL,9,FKyran Smith falsely told staff at the
OL,10,FTravelodge in Maidenhead that they
OL,11,Fwere in a relationship and showed them
OL,12,Fhis ID. He was given a key card,
OL,13,Fentered Emily's room, and attacked her.
OL,15,F"I woke up and I had this person
OL,16,Fliterally in my bed against me. And I
OL,17,Fwas just really confused and I just
OL,18,Fgot out of the bed and sort of like,
OL,19,Fhow did you get into my room?"
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FShe didn't know how long he had been
OL,7,Finside her room before the attack.
OL,9,FIt was the first time Emily was
OL,10,Fstaying in a hotel room alone after an
OL,11,Fevent in December 2022.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FNow, four years later, Smith has been
OL,19,Fjailed for the sexual assault.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FThe impact on Emily's life has been
OL,7,Fhuge.
OL,9,FShe was initially offered an
OL,10,F"insulting" #30 refund from Travelodge
OL,11,Fin compensation, which they later
OL,12,Fadmitted was inappropriate.
OL,14,FBut Emily's anger has been exacerbated
OL,15,Fby the response of the hotel chain
OL,16,Fsince.
OL,18,FGood Morning Britain and ITV News have
OL,19,Fnow learnt Emily met with Chief
OL,20,FExecutive Jo Boydell last week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FBut Emily has told me she left the
OL,7,Fmeeting feeling "deflated" and says
OL,8,Fher actions that night were questioned.
OL,10,F"There was a suggestion from the CEO
OL,11,Fthat the rooms had a deadbolt or
OL,12,Fsomething and I was like, no, even if
OL,13,Fit does, the key obviously overrides
OL,14,Fthat, because I locked my door. I know
OL,15,FI locked my door.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,F"That's deflection in my opinion,
OL,7,Fbecause that's also then saying, 'oh
OL,8,Fwell, hang on a second, you could have
OL,9,Fdone this'. But no, I did everything
OL,10,Fthat I would say is correct and there
OL,11,Fwasn't a chain on the door, there
OL,12,Fwasn't any of that. So her saying that
OL,13,Fkind of just made it worse, in my
OL,14,Fopinion."
OL,16,FIn an interview with me, the hotel
OL,17,Fboss has admitted she was horrified to
OL,18,Flearn about what happened to the
OL,19,Fsurvivor and has apologised for the
OL,20,Fway they have handled the case.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FIn an extraordinary revelation, the
OL,7,Fhotel boss only became aware of the
OL,8,Fincident this month, weeks after Smith
OL,9,Fwas jailed.
OL,11,FJo Boydell told me: "I am absolutely
OL,12,Fhorrified that it had happened in one
OL,13,Fof our hotels, desperately sorry for
OL,14,Fwhat happened to the survivor and
OL,15,Freally sorry for the way that it took
OL,16,Fus so long to actually escalate that
OL,17,Fand handle that properly in the way
OL,18,Fthat we are now."
OL,26,@sD@UOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FWe're meeting in the CEO's office,
OL,7,Fwhich I understand she has barely left
OL,8,Fover the past few weeks.
OL,10,F"I would say I'm really sorry if she
OL,11,F(the survivor) did feel dismissed,"
OL,12,Fsays Ms Boydell.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@ApmsD@NpnsD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,F"And we are definitely listening to
OL,7,Fwhat she (the survivor) has to say,
OL,8,Fwhich is hugely helpful for us in
OL,9,Fterms of making sure that we do the
OL,10,Fright thing going forward. The hotels
OL,11,Fwith key cards have deadbolts, but
OL,12,Fclearly something went wrong here and
OL,13,Fthat needs to be investigated and that
OL,14,Fwill absolutely form part of this
OL,15,Findependent review."
OL,17,FBut Emily felt those in the meeting
OL,18,F"lacked empathy".
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@JpmoD@WpnwD@TO]zD@AOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,F"They're still sort of not really
OL,7,Ftaking full accountability for the
OL,8,Fsituation." she says. "They're not
OL,9,Fdoing enough. If you are the CEO of a
OL,10,Fcompany, in my opinion, if people, MPs
OL,11,Fare asking to meet with you about
OL,12,Fsecurity for women, men, everyone,
OL,13,Fthen why are you not going and why are
OL,14,Fyou not taking that on board?"
OL,16,FMs Boydell met with a handful of
OL,17,Fministers and MPs including
OL,18,FSafeguarding Minister Jess Phillips on
OL,19,FMarch 16.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@KO]pD@WOUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FBut she has been criticised by the
OL,7,Fprime minister for not "seriously
OL,8,Fengaging" with a wider group of
OL,9,Fmembers of parliament.
OL,11,FWhen I asked Ms Boydell how she felt
OL,12,Freceiving the letter from Sir Keir
OL,13,FStarmer, she said "it's obviously not
OL,14,Fsomething that you want to receive".
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@IO]uD@SOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FI asked Emily about the hotel chain
OL,7,Fchanging its room access security
OL,8,Fpolicy which now says "any additional
OL,9,For replacement room keys are only
OL,10,Fissued with explicit permission from
OL,11,Fthe person or people staying in the
OL,12,Froom".
OL,14,F"I was more shocked that that wasn't
OL,15,Ftheir policy anyway," says Emily. "The
OL,16,Ffact that that isn't common sense to
OL,17,Factually have had to get the person's
OL,18,Fconsent before is worse, in my
OL,19,Fopinion, because it's just not enough."
OL,26,@pD@WOUtD@EO]vD@AOUwD@UO]wD@cOU{D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FShe says this incident ought to be a
OL,7,Fwake-up call to all hotels to review
OL,8,Ftheir security policies.
OL,10,F"I think that when you book a hotel,
OL,11,Fif your name isn't on the booking, you
OL,12,Fdon't get a key. If there are
OL,13,Finstances where someone would need a
OL,14,Fkey and they're not on the booking,
OL,15,Fthen you get the consent of that
OL,16,Fperson. That's the only way that it
OL,17,Fworks."
OL,26,@rD@AOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FEmily says she has not stayed in a
OL,7,Fhotel room alone since, and does not
OL,8,Fwish to, describing it as a "mental
OL,9,Fbattle that I need to try and handle".
OL,11,FShe believes until practical changes
OL,12,Fare made and security policies are
OL,13,Fclear cut, an incident like this could
OL,14,Fhappen again.
OL,26,@qD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774894265
OL,3,CSexual assault survivor slams
OL,4,CTravelodge for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,F"Part of my gut reaction would be to
OL,7,Ftake something to block the door. But
OL,8,Fthen I'm like, in my head thinking,
OL,9,Fwell, that's terrible that I even have
OL,10,Fto think like that. And I don't think
OL,11,Fthat's the answer. I don't think that
OL,12,Fis the answer to this. I don't think
OL,13,Fit's a case that I should have to
OL,14,Fbarricade my door. I don't think it's
OL,15,Fright. I think that hotels have to do
OL,16,Fbetter and it's their responsibility
OL,17,Fto make sure they do better."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
